**Terms and Conditions of Fitness Healthy Lifestyle Membership**
Please review the following Terms and Conditions carefully before registering for a membership with Fitness Healthy Lifestyle.
**1. Membership Eligibility:** - By registering for a membership with Fitness Healthy Lifestyle, you affirm that you are at least 18 years old or have obtained parental consent if under 18 years of age. - Membership is non-transferable and may only be used by the registered member.
**2. Membership Fees and Payments:** - Membership fees are outlined in the selected membership plan and are subject to change at the discretion of Fitness Healthy Lifestyle. - Payment is due in full at the time of registration or as otherwise specified in the membership plan. - Membership fees are non-refundable, except as provided under our cancellation policy.
**3. Membership Term and Renewal:** - Membership terms are as specified in the selected membership plan. - Memberships automatically renew at the end of each term unless canceled in accordance with our cancellation policy. - Failure to renew membership may result in the termination of access to Fitness Healthy Lifestyle facilities and services.
**4. Cancellation and Termination:** - Members may cancel their membership at any time by providing written notice to Fitness Healthy Lifestyle. - Refunds for membership fees are subject to the terms outlined in our cancellation policy. - Fitness Healthy Lifestyle reserves the right to terminate or suspend a membership at any time for violation of these Terms and Conditions or for reasons deemed appropriate by Fitness Healthy Lifestyle management.
**5. Facility Access and Code of Conduct:** - Members are granted access to Fitness Healthy Lifestyle facilities during operating hours. - Members must conduct themselves in a respectful manner and adhere to all gym rules and regulations. - Fitness Healthy Lifestyle reserves the right to revoke membership and refuse access to individuals who violate gym rules or engage in inappropriate behavior.
**6. Personal Health and Liability:** - Members are responsible for assessing their own physical condition and consulting with a healthcare professional before participating in any fitness activities. - Fitness Healthy Lifestyle is not liable for any injuries or accidents that occur on gym premises, except in cases of gross negligence or willful misconduct.
**7. Privacy Policy:** - Fitness Healthy Lifestyle respects the privacy of its members and is committed to protecting their personal information. Please refer to our Privacy Policy for details on how we collect, use, and safeguard your information.
**8. Changes to Terms and Conditions:** - Fitness Healthy Lifestyle reserves the right to modify or update these Terms and Conditions at any time without prior notice. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting to our website or notifying members via email.
By registering for a membership with Fitness Healthy Lifestyle, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to abide by these Terms and Conditions.
If you have any questions or concerns regarding these Terms and Conditions, please contact us at [Contact Information].
